Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:20.10,birdy,Assistant,0,0,0,,Pán predseda, prosím poďte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.03,birdy,Assistant,0,0,0,,Slečna Sayaka tiež.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:24.66,birdy,Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Hh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:28.90,birdy,Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Nagaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:34.50,názov kapitoly,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0698F4&\b1}NÁMESAČNÍK{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:57.47,birdy,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,No tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:01.98,birdy,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.84,0:01:28.86,birdy,Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Znova sa to stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:34.19,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,To nie je dobré, zase niet žiadnych svedkov.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.63,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,A stane sa to práve vtedy,\N keď tu je málo cestujúcich.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:39.74,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Zdravím!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:40.17,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.17,0:01:42.17,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Je to už doba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.53,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,Čo je, Muroto?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:46.72,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,Vydal si novú knihu a poslal na veliteľstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:48.04,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,Nie, že by som to čítal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.66,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Nie, nie, dnes je to o inom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:53.23,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Ja sa zaujímam o tento prípad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:57.94,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,Toto je prípad vraždy,\N nie je to jeden z {\i1}tých{\i0} divných príbehov.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.71,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Počkať, počkať počul som nejaké zvesti.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:03.95,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,Áá? Nezmyselný malý príbeh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:06.83,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,Ah a čo pieseň, ktorú bolo počuť?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:07.48,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:13.10,birdy,Student,0,0,0,,Prekliata pieseň, Pieseň Smrti.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.68,birdy,Student,0,0,0,,To je spev z duchovných sfér.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:17.05,birdy,Ryu,0,0,0,,Kliatba?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:18.34,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Pieseň...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:21.55,birdy,Student,0,0,0,,Práve teraz je to na internete hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:27.42,birdy,Student,0,0,0,,V noci počas vraždy,\N bolo počuť z rádia a televízie, ženský spev.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:33.87,note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Poznámka: Toire no Hanako-san je populárny strašidelný príbeh, ktorý sa odohráva v školských toaletách. Teke-teke je horná časť trupu ženy, ktorá hľadá po Japonsku svoju dolnú polovicu. Tá bola oddelená pri železničnej nehode, na ostrove Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:28.83,birdy,Chigira,0,0,0,,Nie je to jedna z tých vecí?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:31.69,birdy,Chigira,0,0,0,,Veci, ako {\b0}Hanako-san{\b1}, alebo {\b0}Teke-Teke{\b1},
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:33.84,birdy,Chigira,0,0,0,,tie boli celkom populárne.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:35.84,birdy,Student,0,0,0,,Tentokrát je to naozaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.85,birdy,Student,0,0,0,,Nahrávka piesne je na celom internete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:40.60,birdy,Kitamura,0,0,0,,Oh, strašidelné!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.81,birdy,Hayamiya,0,0,0,,Kitamura, ty tomu veríš?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:44.85,birdy,Student,0,0,0,,Čo, vy tomu neveríte?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:47.60,birdy,Student,0,0,0,,Ani, keď sa o to zaujíma reportér?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:51.50,birdy,Student,0,0,0,,Nebol tam sempai, ktorý tu chodil do školy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:55.12,birdy,Hayamiya,0,0,0,,Hh? Ten chlap! \NMuroto-senpai vždy hlásal divné veci.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:58.14,birdy,Hayamiya,0,0,0,,Ja pozerám na Sanadu Kaori-sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:01.47,birdy,Hayamiya,0,0,0,,A mňa nezaujímú tieto podivné príbehy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:02.97,birdy,Student,0,0,0,,Podivné príbehy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.39,birdy,Student,0,0,0,,V tom prípade...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:08.68,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Divné príbehy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:11.15,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Vy také na vašej planéte nemáte?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.55,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Či také máme?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.92,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Malý duchovia v chodbách budov...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.20,birdy,Student,0,0,0,,Čo to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.78,birdy,Ryu,0,0,0,,Stiahol si to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:21.07,birdy,Kitamura,0,0,0,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:24.70,birdy,Chigira,0,0,0,,Nenúť nás, počúvať tú pieseň.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:25.97,birdy,Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Hh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.97,birdy,Kitamura,0,0,0,,Bože! Prestaň s tým!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:29.91,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Hh! Nakasugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.48,birdy,Hayamiya,0,0,0,,Héj! Nakasugi, poď, poď!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:41.47,birdy,Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Urobila som to znova.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:43.83,birdy,Girl,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:49.13,birdy,Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Dieťa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.19,birdy,Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Kde si sa tu vzala?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:01.01,birdy,Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Ďakujem, bývaš niekde blízko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:03.80,birdy,Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Ale, nemôžeš vojsť do cudzieho domu, len tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.20,birdy,Girl,0,0,0,,Neboj sa, si v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:09.55,birdy,Girl,0,0,0,,Bola si požehnaná bohyňou ochrany.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.08,birdy,Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Hh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.20,birdy,Reporter,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Z ďalších noviniek:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:30.99,birdy,Reporter,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Doteraz, sa nenašli žiadne stopy, k prípadu vraždy spáchanej v blízkosti linky metra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.99,birdy,Reporter,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Vyšetrovanie je v slepej uličke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:35.96,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nie je to príbeh, o ktorom sme sa rozprávali v škole?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:36.84,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:41.69,birdy,Reporter,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\u0}Všetky obete, mali rozdrvený hrudník a aj orgány.{\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:44.05,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Ako to len urobili?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:45.05,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.01,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hah! Čo chceš robiť?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:55.34,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,No! Čo... prevetrám sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:58.15,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prečo máš na sebe toto oblečenie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.15,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Nestaraj sa o malé detaily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.73,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Trochu ma zaujíma ten prípad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.06,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:05.61,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,No, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:09.43,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Kto si ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.81,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Ja... som... nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.81,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Hmm... Niekde som...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:16.51,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Huh! Áááá! Arita Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:17.59,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:19.45,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ááááááh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:23.85,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Hej, je to pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:26.30,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,O prípade "Prekliata Pieseň".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.54,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Spôsob, ako obete zomreli?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:32.14,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Podľa toho, čo som dnes počul,\N to vyzerá tak, že ich rozdrvila gorila.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:36.65,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Hej, myslím, že by bolo zaujímavé, keby som sa na to pozrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:41.75,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Nemohli by ste to zohľadniť pri financovaní?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.97,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:48.74,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Získam veľa nového materiálu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.09,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Áno. Dobre teda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:55.20,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Yes! Teraz sa môžem najesť.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:06:00.68,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Heh... Myslím, že to nechám tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:06.21,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Som Arita Shion~{\i1} de arudesu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:09.40,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Hahahaha, naozaj vyzeráš ako ona!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.10,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,To je šťastie~ {\i1}de arudesu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:19.27,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Ale to, že si Tsutomu myslel, \Nže by mohol mať priateľku za mojim chrbtom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:22.57,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,No nečakala som, že bude vyzerať rovnako,\N ako Arita Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:24.62,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Teraz tú tvoju hlášku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:28.29,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Rada vás spoznávam~ {\i1}de arudesu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.87,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Hahahaha, vyzeráš presne ako ona!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.75,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hej! Ospravedlň sa a odíť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:35.90,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stále to chceš prešetriť?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.40,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Ja viem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.41,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Nó... Myslím, že je čas, aby som...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.76,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,No, je to tak vzácne, že ťa vidím...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.96,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,No tak ! Daj si, daj si.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.41,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Keď sa napijem môžem odísť?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.33,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Hej, hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.48,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Óó! Óó ~ Óój ~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.26,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Pekný štýl pitia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:05.53,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Potom budem... uh... a... čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:06.73,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Uááh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.42,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Huh? Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:13.40,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Hehehe.... Som v poriadku~ {\i1}desu...{\i0} áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.70,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Si úplne beznádejná.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:24.43,birdy,Girl,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.02,birdy,Girl,0,0,0,,Sranduješ!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:14.63,birdy,Girl,0,0,0,,NIÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉÉ!!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:26.89,birdy,Ryu,0,0,0,,Ha? To myslíš vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:28.37,birdy,Kitamura,0,0,0,,Ale je to pravda!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.52,birdy,Ryu,0,0,0,,Nie je to len nejaký žart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.88,birdy,Kitamura,0,0,0,,Ale, nezomrel niekto včera?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.17,birdy,Kitamura,0,0,0,,Bolo to v tom istom čase.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.63,birdy,Chigira,0,0,0,,Nie je to len taký trik?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:40.24,birdy,Chigira,0,0,0,,Rovnako, ako rušenie rádia a prehrávanie skladieb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.93,birdy,Hayamiya,0,0,0,,Keby to naozaj súviselo s prípadom, tak by to už nehlásili v správach?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:47.50,birdy,Ryu,0,0,0,,Žeby polícia naozaj venovala pozornosť tým fámom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.57,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ak by ma tvoja sestra včera nezdržala...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.63,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Vieš, čo si urobila.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:05.92,birdy,Guy,0,0,0,,Vďaka tým incidentom,\N sme potvrdili približnú polohu páchateľa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.35,birdy,Guy,0,0,0,,Už ju hľadáme.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:10.18,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,To je skvelé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.51,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Ako sa od odborníka dalo očakávať.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:15.30,birdy,Guy,0,0,0,,Avšak, tento prípad nemá nič spoločné s nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:18.38,birdy,Guy,0,0,0,,Nakoniec je to niečo, čo si spôsobil ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:21.81,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Chápem, neboj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:25.69,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Táto krajina je masmédiálna a je ľahké ju manipulovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:35.88,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:40.66,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Prepáčte, ste rodinný príslušník obete?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.27,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Nó, Hah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:42.91,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Hh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:45.29,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Áá! Arita Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:46.81,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Mýliš sa~ {\i1}de arudesu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.58,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Že sa mýlim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:52.20,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prečo je tu Muroto-Senpai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:56.71,birdy,Random person,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:01.25,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Prepáčte mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.59,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Neutečieš mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.79,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Tak kde si Arita Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:25.81,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:31.14,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Ha! Nie je to Muroto-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:35.70,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Hh? Oh! \NNo... ty si Hayamiyin priateľ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:39.71,note,Muruto,0,0,0,,{\an8}Poznámka: Senkawa znamená " Tisíc Riek"\N Ichikawa - "Jedna Rieka" \N Mankawa - "Desaťtisíc Riek.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:38.15,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Ichikawa... No, chlape...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.44,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Som Senkawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.02,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Nó hej, Senkawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:43.83,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Nevidel si tu náhodou vojsť Aritu Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:44.99,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Nevidel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:47.14,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Nikto tu nevstúpil..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:49.00,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Eh? Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.77,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Vidíte ju tu ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.77,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,To je zvláštne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:01.49,birdy,Train,0,0,0,,Ďalšia zastávka, Shinjuku, Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:04.43,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Nuž, toto je moja zastávka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:06.43,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Hej! Počkaj chvíľku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.09,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Haló?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.76,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Tebe tiež? Mohlo by to byť...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:27.14,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Čo urobíme? Birdy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:28.42,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.83,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Hej, Senkawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.07,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Niečo tam je?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:46.46,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:49.59,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Počujem pieseň.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.01,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.73,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,To je strašné.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:16.17,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Hej, Birdy myslíš, že tento prípad má niečo s Ryunkou?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:19.52,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nie som si istá, ale niečo mi na tom vadí.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:22.77,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Ale, myslíš,\N že by Ryunka skutočne zabíjala ľudí?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.65,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\i1}No je to veľmi nebezpečná vec, nie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:28.54,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Určite je pre pozemšťanov nebezpečná.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:30.33,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Možno máš pravdu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:34.24,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Možno to nie je tento prípad, ale treba to preveriť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:34.80,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Mám to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:35.25,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:36.93,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čo je to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.22,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Je to "Stánka Zosnulích".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:40.92,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Je to nepríjemné.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:43.86,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.00,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:46.81,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Nó, týto ľudia...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.65,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,Nemyslíš, že sa veľmi podobajú?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:50.19,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.19,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:56.02,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Všetky obete majú okuliare a nakrátko ostrihané vlasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:04.86,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Idem na to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:28.25,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,Hh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:28.79,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.08,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,Prepáčte mi, slečna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:37.08,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,AAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:37.69,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,ÓÓÓ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.96,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,Muroto!! Čo tu robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:45.08,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Haha. Myslel som si, že keď som takto oblečený,\N tak sa objaví podozrivý.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:45.83,birdy,Muruto,0,0,0,,Hh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.69,birdy,Police,0,0,0,,Čo je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:20.87,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:23.89,birdy,Marionette,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:25.89,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čo je to za vec?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.03,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,Marioneta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:30.42,birdy,Marionette,0,0,0,,Cieľ Potvrdený.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.24,birdy,Staff,0,0,0,,Pán predseda, prosím počkajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.72,birdy,C. Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Ustúp mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:40.43,birdy,C. Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Sasai, čo sa to do pekla deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.11,birdy,C. Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Žiadam vysvetlenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:43.86,birdy,Sasaki,0,0,0,,Pán Predseda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:45.37,birdy,C. Nakasugi,0,0,0,,VY!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:49.61,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Toto nie je dobré pre vaše zdravie, pán Predseda Nakasugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.62,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Pán Sasaki, nepovedali vám to ešte?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.44,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Ste zbabelec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:56.16,birdy,C. Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Shyamalan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:00.31,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Zodpovednosť za vraždy na verejnosti má...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:03.78,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,marioneta, ktorá vám ušla.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.48,birdy,C. Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Marioneta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.36,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Počul ste už o tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:12.34,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Marionety tu vyrobené,\N nie sú len bezpečne prevádzkovaný roboti.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:15.59,birdy,C. Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Nikdy som nepočul,\N aby boli použité, ako bojové stroje.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:19.42,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Naozaj ste si myslel, že boli vyrobené, iba na bezpečné prevádzkovanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.13,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Koľko si myslíte, že som investoval do výskumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.87,birdy,Marionette,0,0,0,,Ma... ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.57,birdy,Marionette,0,0,0,,Cieľ zaistený.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.68,birdy,Marionette,0,0,0,,Ma... ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:40.52,birdy,Marionette,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.40,birdy,Marionette,0,0,0,,Cieľ vymazať.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.16,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,Do riti!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.56,birdy,Marionette,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:49.76,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,No ták!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:51.12,birdy,Marionette,0,0,0,,Vymazať.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:55.39,birdy,C. Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Matka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.92,birdy,Sasaki,0,0,0,,Sú to všetky ženy, ktoré majú rovnaké vlastnosti ako výskumníčka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:00.74,birdy,C. Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Ona ju naprogramovala?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:05.68,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Áno, vyrobila program "Miluj seba ako poklad".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:09.66,birdy,C. Nakasugi,0,0,0,,"N Program" bol úspešne schválený!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.52,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Hej, ale objavila sa chybička.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:17.01,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Nikdy by v reálnom svete nemali šancu, ak by boli vyvinuté podľa vašich snov.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:19.93,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Každý o tom dobre vie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:26.41,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Marionetám "N Program" umožňuje pohyb s vlastnej vôle, niečo, ako čierna skrinka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.95,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Ja som ju len otvoril.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:32.26,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Nie že by som ich dal na vojenský výskum do iných krajín.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.14,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,To tiež dokazuje, že vaši podriadení sú elita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:40.22,birdy,C. Nakasugi,0,0,0,,Kde ste vzal plán na výrobu marionet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:42.62,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Je to lepšie, keď to neviete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:54.72,birdy,Programmer,0,0,0,,Úžasné! \NSpomenieš si na pieseň, ktorú som ťa učila.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:01.66,birdy,Programmer,0,0,0,,Dodré dievča.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:03.24,birdy,Programmer,0,0,0,,Pamätáš si Maminu pieseň?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:06.12,birdy,Marionette,0,0,0,,Ma... ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:10.72,birdy,Programmer,0,0,0,,Som Mama.\N Nemáš ešte kalibrované oči,\N ospravedlňujem sa za to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:14.08,birdy,Programmer,0,0,0,,Milujem ťa, dovoľ mi objať ťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:21.42,birdy,Marionette,0,0,0,,Milujem mamičku, chcem ťa objať.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:27.49,birdy,Marionette,0,0,0,,Ma... ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.24,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Urob to, Birdy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.83,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ak to vyšetrujeme, \Nmali by sme mať nejaké dôkazy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.48,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hej, počúvaš ma?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:06.95,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.06,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,Ah! Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:10.58,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,Máš pravdu. Poďme ju priviesť späť.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:15.86,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čo to bolo?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:16.75,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,Do čerta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:20.80,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,Ochranca?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.49,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,Oni utiekli.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:30.07,birdy,Senkawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čo to teraz bolo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.61,birdy,Birdy,0,0,0,,To bol človek z Federácie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:39.75,birdy,Random Guy,0,0,0,,Slečna, nasledujúci vlak je posledný.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:40.30,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Hhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.78,birdy,Hazumi,0,0,0,,Hhhehe. Ďakujem pekne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:47.75,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Stratil si ju?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.00,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Čo tým myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.53,birdy,Guy,0,0,0,,Práve som dostal od môjho podriadeného správu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:55.48,birdy,Guy,0,0,0,,Zrazu sme stratili signál marionety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:59.27,birdy,Guy,0,0,0,,Už sa nám ho nepodarilo zachytiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.00,birdy,Guy,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje? Čo to bolo za zvuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:09.47,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Našla sa marioneta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:10.12,birdy,Guy,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:23.72,birdy,Fede,0,0,0,,Hrať hry ľudských bábok je dobré, ale treba poriadne upratať.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:30.39,birdy,Fede,0,0,0,,Ak tomu tak nebude, tak ten vzácny poklad po ktorom túžite, vám unikne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.60,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Čo si zač?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.17,birdy,Fede,0,0,0,,Bohyňa Ochrany.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.95,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Neverím v také veci.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.27,birdy,Fede,0,0,0,,Ja tiež nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:19:59.64,birdy,Shamalan,0,0,0,,Mohli by sme byť priatelia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:10.00,birdy,Nakasugi,0,0,0,,To je príjemné.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.68,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Tu je Arita Shion~ {\i1}de arimasu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:19.36,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Ha... Každý deň je horúco~ {\i1}de arimasu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:23.30,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Chystáte sa na chatu v horách teraz v lete, dobrý nápad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:29.76,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Takže! Tsutomu a všetci sa chystajú na chatu Nakasugi~ {\i1}de arimasu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:33.72,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Srdce Tsutomua zrejme búši vzrušením!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:40.00,birdy,Shion,0,0,0,,Ale, dobré počasie zabráni nebezpečným udalostiam. \NGuáááá~
